Package contactsmanager

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Contact
    A contact is a person we are making business with or may do in the future.
    ContactManager
    A class to manage your contacts and meetings.
    ContactManagerDesired
    A class to manage your contacts and meetings.
    DataStore
    A class to serialise the data stored in ContactManager to be saved to file, and also deserialise data stored in a file for use in ContactManager.
    FutureMeeting
    A meeting to be held in the future.
    Meeting
    A class to represent meetings.
    PastMeeting
    A meeting that was held in the past.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMeeting
    An abstract implementation of Meeting.
    ContactImpl
    An implementation of Contact.
    ContactManagerImpl
    An implementation of ContactManager.
    FutureMeetingImpl
    An implementation of AbstractMeeting.
    PastMeetingImpl
    An implementation of PastMeeting, extending AbstractMeeting by allowing notes to be added.
    XmlDataStore
    An implementation of DataStore that loads and saves data in xml files.
